OL,3,CWarning over health workers' pay rise
OL,4,Cpledge
OL,6,FRelentless demand and constant
OL,7,Fpressure. That's the reality for
OL,8,FNorthern Ireland's health workers.
OL,10,FThey have been promised a pay rise,
OL,11,Fbut yesterday, officials warned the
OL,12,Fhealth committee that sticking to that
OL,13,Fcommitment will be a challenge without
OL,14,Fa multi-year budget.
OL,16,FDavid Keenan, Department of Health,
OL,17,Fsaid: "It still remains the minister's
OL,18,Fcommitment. How it'll be funded will
OL,19,Fbe the difficulty."
