OL,6,FFor those who have long fought for
OL,7,Ffair pay, failing to honour that
OL,8,Fcommitment would be unthinkable.
OL,10,FRita Devlin, Royal College of Nurses
OL,11,FNorthern Ireland, said: "My concern
OL,12,Fwould be what's stopping the budget
OL,13,Ffrom being agreed?
OL,15,F"We will not sit back and let our
OL,16,FExecutive once again fight over what
OL,17,Fshould actually be happening in order
OL,18,Ffor our, our health service, our
OL,19,Feducation service, and all the other
OL,20,Fservices that people need.
