OL,6,F"We won't sit back and let that happen
OL,7,Fagain."
OL,9,FDelivering on that pay comes as the
OL,10,Fsystem strains on multiple fronts,
OL,11,Flike waiting lists, ambulance delays,
OL,12,Fcorridor care, and delayed discharges.
OL,14,FTo tackle these, the Health Service
OL,15,FLeadership Centre brings in former NHS
OL,16,Ffigures to drive reform and fix
OL,17,Fsystemic problems.
