OL,6,FIn five years, spending on the centre
OL,7,Fhas more than doubled, from #3m to
OL,8,F#6.5m. As of July 2025, 326
OL,9,Fconsultants were on its books.
OL,11,FFOI data also shows that 230 are
OL,12,Fformer members of a health and social
OL,13,Fcare body, but their identities have
OL,14,Fnot been disclosed.
OL,16,FDetailed information on targets,
OL,17,Fperformance measures, and outcomes
OL,18,Fremains limited, prompting questions
OL,19,Fabout transparency and value for money.
