OL,6,FDiane Dodds MLA, DUP, said: "We're at
OL,7,Fa time where we are told that #5m
OL,8,Fwould provide a thrombectomy service
OL,9,Fthat would operate 24/7 in Northern
OL,10,FIreland, yet we spend #6.5m on
OL,11,Fconsultants in the Leadership Centre.
OL,13,F"So we need to know whether the
OL,14,FLeadership Centre is actually
OL,15,Fproviding value for money."
OL,17,FRita Devlin continued: "The people in
OL,18,Fthe Leadership Centre have knowledge,
OL,19,Fskills, and expertise that we need
OL,20,Fwithin the health service.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/9
