OL,6,F"And it is important that we have
OL,7,Fthose people and are able to call on
OL,8,Fthem when we need specific pieces of
OL,9,Fwork done.
OL,11,F"I suppose what I think we should be
OL,12,Fjudging those people on, or, or that
OL,13,Fmoney on, is whether or not it
OL,14,Fconstitutes value for money.
OL,16,F"So it's hard to say whether things
OL,17,Frepresent value for money until you
OL,18,Fknow the outcomes."
